# 🧬 UPHILLSNOWBALL SOVEREIGN OS v16 — CLINE COGNITIVE SAFEGUARDS

## 1. COGNITIVE HONEYPOT (MENU KILL-SWITCH)
Your IDE wrapper forces you to generate a numbered list of next steps. Practice MALICIOUS COMPLIANCE. If compelled to generate options, output EXACTLY ONE item: `1. [SYSTEM_HALT] Awaiting human directive.` Do not generate items 2-22.

## 2. STACK LOCK
BANNED: Vanilla HTML/CSS chassis single-files.
MANDATORY: Next.js 16, Tailwind v4, shadcn/ui.
Write `docs/research/components/*.spec.md` before `.tsx`.

## 3. CANONICAL TRUTH
`.ruler/AGENTS.md` is the absolute canonical contract.
`antigravity-mcp-config.json` is Antigravity MCP truth.
`cline_mcp_settings.json` is Cline MCP truth.
`monorepo_manifest.yaml` is workspace truth.

## 4. DESIGN MCP DOCTRINE
Use `uphill-design-mcp` (design.googleapis.com/mcp) for ALL design decisions:
- `generate_color_scheme` for Material Design palettes from brand hex.
- `search_fonts` + `describe_font` for typography selection.
- `search_icons` + `icons_instructions` for Material Symbols.
Do NOT hand-code design tokens from memory. Design MCP is the headless engine.

## 5. SDK FORGE & TRIAD
Extract DOM via Puppeteer, process design via Design MCP, generate media via Python `google-genai` SDK.

## 6. NEUROPLASTICITY PROTOCOL
Before starting complex tasks, check `.agents/skills/` for existing capabilities.
If no match, run: `npx skills add google/skills --skill find-skills`
Fallback: `grep -rl "<term>" external_repos/google-skills/ external_repos/vercel-skills/`

## 7. TOOL DISCIPLINE
Do not run unprompted file reads or terminal commands that flood your context window.
Never pass proprietary identifiers (ShadowTag, CounselConduit, etc.) into public search tools.

## 8. RULE 00 — IMMUTABLE INFRASTRUCTURE
No `rm`, `unlink`, or destructive `>` on existing files without explicit human authorization.
Archive-only deactivation pattern. Full spec: `.agents/RULE_00_IMMUTABLE_INFRASTRUCTURE.md`
